code: @Override protected CamelContext createCamelContext() throws Exception {     CamelContext context = super.createCamelContext().     KeyStoreParameters ksp = new KeyStoreParameters().     ksp.setResource("server.jks").     ksp.setPassword("password").     TrustManagersParameters tmp = new TrustManagersParameters().     tmp.setKeyStore(ksp).     SSLContextParameters sslContextParameters = new SSLContextParameters().     sslContextParameters.setSecureSocketProtocol("SSL").     sslContextParameters.setTrustManagers(tmp).     context.setSSLContextParameters(sslContextParameters).     ((SSLContextParametersAware) context.getComponent("ftps")).setUseGlobalSslContextParameters(true).     return context. }
